  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BatchDataTableScan

    Factory to create BatchDataTableScan.

    Inner TableScan contains filter push down.

    An interface for building the TableScan and TableRead.

    An input split for reading.

    Generate splits from DataFileMetas.

    DataTableScan for streaming planning.
    StreamDataTableScan.Factory
    Factory to create StreamDataTableScan.

    TableScan for streaming, supports Restorable.checkpoint() and Restorable.restore(S).
    TableRead
    An abstraction layer above FileStoreRead to provide reading of InternalRow.
